Subject: [PATCH 0206/1221] MLK-10447-03: ARM: imx_v7_defconfig: Add spi gpio
 and gpio 74x164

Enable CONFIG_SPI_GPIO and CONFIG_GPIO_74X164 to imx_v7_defconfig.

Signed-off-by: Sandor Yu <R01008@freescale.com>
[zou:Original patch taken from
git.freescale.com/imx/fsl-arm-yocto-bsp.git-b imx-3.14.52-1.1.0_ga]
Signed-off-by: zou cao <cao.zou@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm/configs/imx_v7_defconfig |    2 ++
 1 files changed, 2 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/configs/imx_v7_defconfig b/arch/arm/configs/imx_v7_defconfig
index 7842266..5fbffd6 100644
--- a/arch/arm/configs/imx_v7_defconfig
+++ b/arch/arm/configs/imx_v7_defconfig
@@ -183,9 +183,11 @@ CONFIG_I2C_ALGOPCF=m
 CONFIG_I2C_ALGOPCA=m
 CONFIG_I2C_IMX=y
 CONFIG_SPI=y
+CONFIG_SPI_GPIO=y
 CONFIG_SPI_IMX=y
 CONFIG_GPIO_SYSFS=y
 CONFIG_POWER_SUPPLY=y
+CONFIG_GPIO_74X164=y
 CONFIG_SABRESD_MAX8903=y
 CONFIG_SENSORS_MAX17135=y
 CONFIG_IMX6_USB_CHARGER=y
